comments: That moment when you’re so proud that you’re almost done… and then Chris says “alright that was the warm up.”

1:27 butt kicks
2:27 burpees
3:27 jamping jacks
4:27 switching lunges
5:27 squat taps
6:27 switching mountain climber
7:27 shoulder to shoulder
8:27 seated in & out
9:28 seated leg flutters
10:28 bicycles
This workout is so intensive that you will start liking YouTube ads ( they give you some extra break 😅)

I've been doing this for a couple of weeks now & it seems a lot easier compared to the day I started.
If you are feeling the same just remember one thing, 'it’s not getting easier, you are getting stronger'
I've done this workout (three sets)  every day for the last two months and lost more than 22 pounds, thank you Chris!!
